'''Kishi''' was an area of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] near [[Westport]] that contained the [[Pillar Zone]]. In [[19 BBY/Legends|19.9 BBY]], after the crash of an infected ship called the ''[[Spinner]]'', Kishi became overrun with [[Stone mite/Legends|stone mites]]. However, [[Jedi healer/Legends|Jedi healers]] used [[Morichro/Legends|morichro]] to destroy the infestation.

